text: Altyntash () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilchigulovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 13 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 73 km from Uchaly, 16 km from Ilchigulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Altyntash
